# 控制器规范

## 命名规则

| 项目 | 规则 | 示例 |
|------|------|------|
| 文件名 | `{资源名}_controller.py` | `user_controller.py` |
| 类名 | `{资源名}Controller` | `UserController` |
| 路径 | `/{分组}/{资源名}` | `/api/user` |
| 标签 | `{分组}API - {功能}` | `API - 用户管理` |

## API分组

| 分组 | 前缀 | 标签 |
|------|------|------|
| AdminAPI | `/admin/*` | `AdminAPI - {功能}` |
| API | `/api/*` | `API - {功能}` |
| WebAPI | `/web/*` | `WebAPI - {功能}` |

## 示例

```python
# app/controller/api/user_controller.py
from app.core.controllers.base_controller import *

@api_controller(prefix="/api/user", tags=["API - 用户管理"])
class UserController(BaseController):
    
    @get("/list", summary="获取列表")
    async def get_users(self, request: Request) -> Response:
        pass
    
    @post("/create", summary="创建")
    async def create_user(self, request: Request) -> Response:
        pass
    
    @put("/{id}", summary="更新")
    async def update_user(self, request: Request, id: str) -> Response:
        pass
    
    @delete("/{id}", summary="删除")
    async def delete_user(self, request: Request, id: str) -> Response:
        pass
```

## RESTful

| 操作 | 方法 | 路径 |
|------|------|------|
| 列表 | GET | `/list` |
| 详情 | GET | `/{id}` |
| 创建 | POST | `/create` |
| 更新 | PUT | `/{id}` |
| 删除 | DELETE | `/{id}` |
